Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.64,0:01:34.81,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:90645,94816}{\i1}17 years ago, Kōda Miki and Mine Nozomi,\Nwho were born in the same hospital,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.81,0:01:39.23,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:94816,99237}{\i1}had been swapped by Nohara Michiko,\Nwho held a grudge against the upper class.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.23,0:01:44.90,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:99237,104909}{\i1}Learning that Mine Nozomi was the rightful heiress\Nto the Kōda family was a huge shock for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.90,0:01:47.28,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:104909,107286}{\i1}Nozomi, to whom\Nit hasn't fully sunk in yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.28,0:01:49.62,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:107286,109622}{\i1}now also learns that her father\Nis in a critical condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.83,0:01:52.83,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:110832,112834}Hello? Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.71,0:01:56.46,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:114711,116462}Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.46,0:01:58.13,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:116462,118131}So he's in hospital now?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.13,0:02:04.17,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:119132,124178}Yes, I asked Kuma-san to carry him\Nto the hospital. It looked very serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.17,0:02:08.14,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:124178,128141}The doctors have told me that\Nhe was suffering this whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.72,0:02:12.35,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:128725,132353}{\i1}Had he said anything before,\Nmaybe we could do something about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.89,0:02:17.15,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:133896,137150}But you know how stubborn he is.\NHe's been suffering through this all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.81,0:02:20.61,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:137817,140611}Don't lose hope, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.61,0:02:22.69,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:140611,142697}He's in the hospital now,\Nthey're going to save him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.69,0:02:23.94,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:142697,143948}You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.32,0:02:27.16,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:145325,147160}Are you still working?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.74,0:02:29.66,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:147744,149662}Yes. We're going live in a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.53,0:02:33.20,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:150538,153207}Try to focus only on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.20,0:02:37.67,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:153207,157670}I'll do what I can to make Dad\Nhold on until you can see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.46,0:02:39.54,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:158463,159547}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.54,0:02:41.42,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:159547,161424}{\i1}All right, I'm hanging up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.42,0:02:43.42,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:161424,163426}Ah! Mom…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.01,0:02:49.68,Default,[title],0,0,0,,{TIME:166012,169682}{\fad(0,1500)}— Episode 25 —\NGoodbye, Dad{NOTE:第25話\\N父との別れ}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.43,0:02:53.64,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:172435,173644}Dad…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.81,0:02:56.31,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:174812,176314}You can't die on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.31,0:02:57.02,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:176314,177023}Don't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.02,0:02:58.69,Default,Staff,0,0,0,,{TIME:177023,178691}Mine-san. Mine-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.69,0:02:59.40,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:178691,179400}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.40,0:03:01.94,Default,Staff,0,0,0,,{TIME:179400,181944}We're going live in a minute.\NPlease get ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.94,0:03:04.57,Default,Staff,0,0,0,,{TIME:181944,184572}Oh? You look pale.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.57,0:03:06.03,Default,Staff,0,0,0,,{TIME:184572,186032}Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.03,0:03:07.70,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:186032,187700}No, not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.70,0:03:10.07,Default,Staff,0,0,0,,{TIME:187700,190078}Put a bit more make-up\Nand you should be good to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.07,0:03:11.99,Default,Staff,0,0,0,,{TIME:190078,191996}Ah, Hara-san, wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.79,0:03:16.95,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:193790,196959}Dad, hang in there.\NI'll see you soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.21,0:03:24.21,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:200213,204217}{\fad(1500,0)\an2}Rehearsal  ·  Live{NOTE:リハーサル\\N本番中}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.67,0:03:26.05,Default,Staff,0,0,0,,{TIME:204675,206052}Ten seconds to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.05,0:03:28.13,Default,Staff,0,0,0,,{TIME:207053,208137}Eight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.01,0:03:30.30,Default,Staff,0,0,0,,{TIME:209013,210306}Five.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.93,0:03:32.14,Default,Staff,0,0,0,,{TIME:210932,212141}Three.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.43,0:03:33.39,Default,Staff,0,0,0,,{TIME:212433,213393}Ready…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.39,0:03:34.31,Default,Staff,0,0,0,,{TIME:213393,214310}Start!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.81,0:03:41.06,Default,Host,0,0,0,,{TIME:216813,221067}Ladies and gentlemen, good evening and\Nwelcome to the Star Parade you all waited for.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.06,0:03:46.78,Default,Host,0,0,0,,{TIME:221067,226781}Last week we introduced you to a girl who aroused\Na wave of admiration all over the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.78,0:03:51.99,Default,Host,0,0,0,,{TIME:226781,231994}We received a mountain of letters from her\Nnumerous admirers and we're very pleased
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.99,0:03:54.43,Default,Host,0,0,0,,{TIME:231994,234430}to present Nozomi-san\Ntoday to you as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.83,0:03:58.04,Default,Host,0,0,0,,{TIME:235832,238042}Well then, let's hear her sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.04,0:03:59.41,Default,Host,0,0,0,,{TIME:238042,239419}Mine-san, the screen's all yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.12,0:04:02.00,Default,Host,0,0,0,,{TIME:240128,242004}She'll sing us the "Song of Heart".
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.99,0:04:31.86,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:269991,271868}Dad. Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.86,0:04:33.36,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:271868,273369}Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.49,0:04:39.12,Default,Nurse,0,0,0,,{TIME:277498,279125}– Say…\N– Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.12,0:04:40.58,Default,Nurse,0,0,0,,{TIME:279125,280585}About that girl on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.58,0:04:41.66,Default,Nurse,0,0,0,,{TIME:280585,281669}Isn't she Mine Nozomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.66,0:04:44.25,Default,Nurse,0,0,0,,{TIME:281669,284255}She's the daughter\Nof the patient from 203.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.25,0:04:46.63,Default,Nurse,0,0,0,,{TIME:284255,286632}But looks like she's actually not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.63,0:04:47.30,Default,Nurse,0,0,0,,{TIME:286632,287300}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.30,0:04:49.46,Default,Nurse,0,0,0,,{TIME:287300,289469}– You know Kōda Miki, right?\N– Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.46,0:04:54.26,Default,Nurse,0,0,0,,{TIME:289469,294265}In reality, she's the real daughter\Nof Mine-san, rather than Mine Nozomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.26,0:04:56.80,Default,Nurse,0,0,0,,{TIME:294265,296809}Rumor has it that the two of them\Nwere swapped at birth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.80,0:05:01.23,Default,Nurse,0,0,0,,{TIME:296809,301230}Anyway, don't you think it's heartless to sing\Non television while your father's dying?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.23,0:05:04.15,Default,Nurse,0,0,0,,{TIME:301230,304150}This kind of attitude is typical\Namong artists, to be honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.15,0:05:08.77,Default,Nurse,0,0,0,,{TIME:304150,308779}Parents of famous people often\Ndie alone without anyone by their bedside.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.28,0:05:10.65,Default,Nurse,0,0,0,,{TIME:309280,310656}You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.65,0:05:11.99,Default,Nurse,0,0,0,,{TIME:310656,311991}That's the way it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.07,0:05:15.95,Default,Nurse,0,0,0,,{TIME:315077,315953}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.95,0:05:18.70,Default,Doctor,0,0,0,,{TIME:315953,318706}Please come to the room 203.\NThere's something wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.62,0:05:20.95,Default,Nurse,0,0,0,,{TIME:319624,320958}Right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.62,0:05:58.82,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:357620,358829}Dad…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.83,0:06:00.83,Default,Taxi driver,0,0,0,,{TIME:359830,360831}Did anything happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.95,0:06:03.70,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:361958,363709}No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.70,0:06:05.29,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:363709,365294}But let's go faster, if possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.29,0:06:06.58,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:365294,366587}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.58,0:06:07.67,Default,Taxi driver,0,0,0,,{TIME:366587,367672}Sure thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.93,0:06:21.60,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:379934,381602}Where can I find\NMine Shinsuke's room?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.60,0:06:23.27,Default,Receptionist,0,0,0,,{TIME:381602,383271}Second floor, room 203.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.82,0:06:35.19,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:393823,395199}{\i1}Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.25,0:06:52.30,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:411257,412300}Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.73,0:07:12.86,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:431736,432862}Dad…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.36,0:07:20.66,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:439368,440661}Nozomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.66,0:07:23.66,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:440661,443664}He kept calling your name\Nuntil the very end.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.24,0:07:25.37,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:444248,445374}Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.49,0:08:03.24,Default,Nurse,0,0,0,,{TIME:481494,483245}Look, that's Mine Nozomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.24,0:08:07.24,Default,Nurse,0,0,0,,{TIME:483245,487249}The artists never arrive in time.\NThey never remember about their family…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.62,0:08:11.33,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:489627,491337}Nozomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.33,0:08:12.75,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:491337,492755}Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.75,0:08:14.17,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:492755,494173}Yes, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.19,0:08:34.61,Default,Paparazzi,0,0,0,,{TIME:512191,514610}And? Are they still up?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.61,0:08:36.52,Default,Paparazzi,0,0,0,,{TIME:514610,516529}Yeah, the light's still on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.52,0:08:39.07,Default,Paparazzi,0,0,0,,{TIME:516529,519073}Looks like the family meeting's still on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.86,0:08:44.53,Default,Paparazzi,0,0,0,,{TIME:519865,524537}Maybe we might even take a nice photo of Kōda\NMiki with the saddest expression in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.53,0:08:45.95,Default,Paparazzi,0,0,0,,{TIME:524537,525955}Yeah. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.95,0:08:47.70,Default,Paparazzi,0,0,0,,{TIME:525955,527707}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.45,0:08:49.83,Default,Landlady,0,0,0,,{TIME:528457,529834}Is someone there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.62,0:08:52.50,Default,Landlady,0,0,0,,{TIME:531627,532503}Weird…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.50,0:08:53.96,Default,Kōda Daijirō,0,0,0,,{TIME:532503,533963}What's the matter, Hiroko?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.58,0:08:57.88,Default,Landlady,0,0,0,,{TIME:534588,537883}Oh, it's you, Master?\NI thought I heard someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.88,0:09:00.34,Default,Kōda Daijirō,0,0,0,,{TIME:537883,540344}Make sure every door stays locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.34,0:09:01.05,Default,Landlady,0,0,0,,{TIME:540344,541053}Naturally.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.22,0:09:09.68,Default,Kōda Daijirō,0,0,0,,{TIME:545224,549687}It must be recognized that you are\Npartly responsible for all this, my dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.68,0:09:11.43,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:549687,551439}What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.43,0:09:16.40,Default,Kōda Daijirō,0,0,0,,{TIME:551439,556402}You were so worried about bad rumors,\Nthat you tried to buy all the journalists.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.40,0:09:18.32,Default,Kōda Daijirō,0,0,0,,{TIME:556402,558320}But money doesn't solve everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.32,0:09:20.15,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:558320,560156}But what else could I have done?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.15,0:09:23.53,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:560156,563534}Realistically speaking,\NI hardly had any alternatives.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.53,0:09:27.20,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:563534,567204}Why don't you put yourself\Nin our place, for once?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.20,0:09:31.33,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:567204,571333}Staying all day long locked in the house,\Nunable to go out. What an insistent bunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.33,0:09:35.33,Default,Kōda Daijirō,0,0,0,,{TIME:571333,575337}Well, you can't deny that you yourself\Ntried to corrupt the press.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.79,0:09:38.59,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:576797,578591}Watch how you talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.13,0:09:44.63,Default,Landlady,0,0,0,,{TIME:582136,584638}Master, someone named\NKumagorō is calling.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.30,0:09:46.34,Default,Kōda Daijirō,0,0,0,,{TIME:585306,586348}Kumagorō?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.34,0:09:48.14,Default,Kōda Daijirō,0,0,0,,{TIME:586348,588142}Hmm. I wonder who he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.93,0:09:54.69,Default,Kōda Daijirō,0,0,0,,{TIME:591937,594690}Hello? This is Kōda. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.69,0:09:55.35,Default,Kōda Daijirō,0,0,0,,{TIME:594690,595357}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.35,0:09:58.27,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:595357,598277}Well, just now, err…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.27,0:10:01.07,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:598277,601071}Nozomi-chan's father…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.07,0:10:04.11,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:601071,604116}I mean, the father of\NMiki-san from your house…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.11,0:10:09.16,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:604116,609163}Actually I don't know how you're related,\Nbut someone just has to tell you about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.16,0:10:10.24,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:609163,610247}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.79,0:10:14.00,Default,Kōda Daijirō,0,0,0,,{TIME:610790,614001}Oh, I see.\NThank you for letting us know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.00,0:10:15.25,Default,Kōda Daijirō,0,0,0,,{TIME:614001,615252}Thank you. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.25,0:10:18.25,Default,Kōda Daijirō,0,0,0,,{TIME:615252,618255}We'll definitely come\Nfor the incense offering.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.18,0:10:29.26,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:628182,629266}What was that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.35,0:10:33.60,Default,Kōda Daijirō,0,0,0,,{TIME:630351,633604}A man called Kuma-san\Nsaid over the phone…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.98,0:10:37.35,Default,Kōda Daijirō,0,0,0,,{TIME:634980,637358}…that Nozomi-san's father\Nhas passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.52,0:10:42.73,Default,Kōda Daijirō,0,0,0,,{TIME:639527,642738}Of course, he was also\NMiki's biological father.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.61,0:10:44.86,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:643614,644865}Hey, now…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.99,0:10:49.62,Default,Kōda Daijirō,0,0,0,,{TIME:648994,649620}Miki.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.03,0:10:52.28,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:650037,652289}No! I'm not going anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.28,0:10:54.45,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:652289,654458}I'm not going to his funeral!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.71,0:11:01.42,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:657711,661423}He's not my real dad.\NIt's all wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.97,0:11:06.92,Default,Kōda Daijirō,0,0,0,,{TIME:665970,666929}Miki.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.92,0:11:09.34,Default,Kōda Daijirō,0,0,0,,{TIME:666929,669348}I understand how you're feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.34,0:11:10.85,Default,Kōda Daijirō,0,0,0,,{TIME:669348,670850}It isn't easy for me, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.80,0:11:15.85,Default,Kōda Daijirō,0,0,0,,{TIME:671809,675855}For 17 years, you have been my daughter,\Nand now suddenly you're a child of a stranger.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.18,0:11:18.35,Default,Kōda Daijirō,0,0,0,,{TIME:677189,678357}But listen to me, Miki.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.35,0:11:23.19,Default,Kōda Daijirō,0,0,0,,{TIME:678357,683195}There are things that we cannot change.\NWe must face bravely whatever life has in store.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.19,0:11:26.86,Default,Kōda Daijirō,0,0,0,,{TIME:683195,686866}It is the only thing\Nus humans can do to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.99,0:11:29.86,Default,Kōda Daijirō,0,0,0,,{TIME:687992,689869}I would say that is more\Nthan enough for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.86,0:11:32.87,Default,Kōda Daijirō,0,0,0,,{TIME:689869,692872}Tomorrow we'll pay tribute\Nto Nozomi-san's father.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.70,0:11:38.79,Default,Kōda Daijirō,0,0,0,,{TIME:695708,698794}This means we'll also meet\Nyour biological mother, Miki.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.79,0:11:42.13,Default,Kōda Daijirō,0,0,0,,{TIME:698794,702131}We'll all have to think about\Nhow to make the best of this situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.25,0:11:45.67,Default,Kōda Daijirō,0,0,0,,{TIME:703257,705676}Of course, without neglecting\Nyour brilliant career.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.67,0:11:47.88,Default,Kōda Daijirō,0,0,0,,{TIME:705676,707887}There's nothing to be afraid of.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.63,0:11:49.97,Default,Kōda Daijirō,0,0,0,,{TIME:708637,709972}Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.97,0:11:54.35,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:712975,714351}Dear…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.65,0:12:04.77,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:723652,724778}Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.24,0:12:18.66,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:735247,738667}{\i1}They're all trying to deceive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.66,0:12:20.50,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:738667,740502}{\i1}Even Mom and Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.50,0:12:26.21,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:740502,746216}{\i1}Now that Daddy knows that I'm\Nnot his daughter, he'll hate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.21,0:12:29.47,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:746216,749470}{\i1}He'll just take Nozomi in\Nand drive me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.05,0:12:35.76,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:753057,755768}{\i1}My life is destroyed.
Comment: 0,0:12:40.28,0:12:40.28,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:760289,760289}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.51,0:12:46.89,Default,Landlady,0,0,0,,{TIME:763517,766895}Ma'am, your father has asked me\Nto come to wake you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.89,0:12:48.89,Default,Landlady,0,0,0,,{TIME:766895,768897}You're going out together, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.61,0:12:53.90,Default,Landlady,0,0,0,,{TIME:772610,773902}Ma'am?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.90,0:12:54.48,Default,Landlady,0,0,0,,{TIME:773902,774486}Ma—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.36,0:13:04.24,Default,Landlady,0,0,0,,{TIME:782369,784246}Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.24,0:13:05.83,Default,Landlady,0,0,0,,{TIME:784246,785831}Something horrible happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.41,0:13:07.87,Default,Kōda Daijirō,0,0,0,,{TIME:786415,787875}"I'm leaving this house".
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.87,0:13:08.95,Default,Kōda Daijirō,0,0,0,,{TIME:787875,788959}"Miki".
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.25,0:13:12.33,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:791253,792338}What should we do, dear?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.33,0:13:15.04,Default,Kōda Daijirō,0,0,0,,{TIME:793339,795049}There's nothing we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.04,0:13:16.34,Default,Kōda Daijirō,0,0,0,,{TIME:795049,796342}Let's call the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.38,0:13:18.34,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:797384,798344}Police?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.71,0:13:20.22,Default,Kōda Daijirō,0,0,0,,{TIME:798719,800220}Yes. The sooner, the better.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.22,0:13:22.22,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:800220,802222}But isn't it a bit too much?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.22,0:13:23.59,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:802222,803599}If we involve the police…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.59,0:13:26.35,Default,Kōda Daijirō,0,0,0,,{TIME:803599,806352}This is the only way we can find Miki.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.48,0:13:34.44,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:811482,814443}Who would've thought that\Nwe'd have reached this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.44,0:13:35.69,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:814443,815694}This is the end of our family.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.69,0:13:39.78,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:815694,819782}Now people will come to believe\Nwhat all the newspapers write about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.11,0:13:39.78,Default,Kōda Daijirō,0,0,0,,{TIME:818113,819782}{\an8}Hello? Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.78,0:13:41.49,Default,Kōda Daijirō,0,0,0,,{TIME:819782,821492}{\an8}Our daughter has gone—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.49,0:13:44.49,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:821492,824495}Mine{NOTE:峰家}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.46,0:14:02.51,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:840469,842513}I prepared you something to eat, Nozomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.64,0:14:09.14,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:846642,849144}It's not good for your health\Nif you continue like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.14,0:14:11.23,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:849144,851230}You didn't eat anything\Nsince yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.23,0:14:13.35,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:851230,853357}Please, just eat something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.86,0:14:18.52,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:856860,858529}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.90,0:14:23.65,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:861907,863659}I decided to stop singing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.20,0:14:27.16,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:864201,867162}Starting today,\NI'll find something else to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.16,0:14:28.66,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:867162,868664}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.66,0:14:29.66,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:868664,869665}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.66,0:14:35.00,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:873669,875003}Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.00,0:14:39.17,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:875003,879174}Because I was singing on television,\NI arrived too late at Dad's bedside.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.05,0:14:43.92,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:880050,883929}I didn't have the chance to say goodbye\Nto the most important person in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.92,0:14:45.68,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:883929,885681}I'll never forgive myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.22,0:14:49.10,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:887224,889101}I'll never forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.64,0:14:53.68,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:891645,893689}I'm sorry, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.44,0:14:56.69,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:894440,896692}Dad… I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.35,0:14:59.73,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:897359,899737}Nozomi, you got it all wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.73,0:15:02.69,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:899737,902698}In all your life, you had never\Ndisappointed your dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.15,0:15:05.99,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:903157,905993}On the contrary,\Nhe's been very proud of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.99,0:15:10.83,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:905993,910831}He'd been telling everyone about how his\Ndaughter was going to become a great singer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.83,0:15:13.83,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:910831,913834}That's not the only reason, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.83,0:15:17.33,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:913834,917337}What good are my songs\Nthat I sing on television
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.33,0:15:22.76,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:917337,922760}if I fail as a human being\Nat the most important things?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.76,0:15:25.72,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:922760,925721}My songs can't save anyone's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.72,0:15:27.97,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:925721,927973}They're just empty,\Nmeaningless words.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.76,0:15:33.31,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:928766,933312}I'm sorry, Mom, but I have\Nno intention of continuing to sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.31,0:15:35.98,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:933312,935981}Forgive me, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.98,0:15:38.98,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:935981,938984}I don't want to lose Mom\Nthe way I lost you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.36,0:15:41.61,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:940360,941612}Nozomi…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.44,0:15:44.15,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:943447,944156}Nozomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.65,0:15:48.49,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:945657,948494}I'm going to get rid of this guitar.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.99,0:15:50.49,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:948994,950496}Hold on, Nozomi! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.83,0:15:53.08,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:951830,953081}Gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.95,0:15:56.25,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:953957,956251}This is the one thing\NI can't let you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.25,0:15:58.21,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:956251,958212}Please, let go of me, Kuma-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.21,0:15:59.58,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:958212,959588}No can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.58,0:16:00.88,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:959588,960881}I can't let you do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.88,0:16:03.59,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:960881,963592}I'm here to stop you,\Nas your number one fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.17,0:16:07.80,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:964176,967805}Kuma-san, I decided that I'll never\Nsing or use this guitar again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.80,0:16:12.60,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:967805,972601}How could I, after I've betrayed my father,\Nnot even keeping him company on his deathbed?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.31,0:16:16.60,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:973310,976605}You're looking at this from the wrong side.\NThink about it this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.94,0:16:20.60,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:977940,980609}Listen close, Nozomi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.19,0:16:24.73,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:981193,984738}Everyone knows I'm not very smart\Nand I don't understand the difficult stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.73,0:16:30.74,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:984738,990744}But one thing I know for sure is that I love your\Nmusic and I'd like to continue to hear you sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.74,0:16:34.41,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:990744,994414}You see, when I hear you sing,\NI kinda forget about all the problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.41,0:16:37.16,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:994414,997167}It's like, I feel I can do anything\Nand things will be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.87,0:16:39.67,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:997876,999670}And it's not just me, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.67,0:16:41.79,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:999670,1001797}Your dad was like that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.79,0:16:44.17,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1001797,1004174}Everyone loves your songs,\NNozomi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.25,0:16:47.26,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1005259,1007261}Your dad once told me:
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.26,0:16:49.84,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1007261,1009847}"Nozomi is going\Nto become a great singer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.84,0:16:55.68,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1009847,1015686}You know why? Because I have a tin ear,\Nyet when she sings, it does something to me."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.06,0:17:00.77,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1018063,1020774}I don't think he had tin ear, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.56,0:17:08.78,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1022568,1028782}Nozomi-chan, I'm sure your dad went\Nup to heaven hearing your music.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.78,0:17:11.07,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1028782,1031076}You sing so well, with so much love!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.07,0:17:13.87,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1031076,1033871}It's impossible he didn't hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.87,0:17:15.78,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1033871,1035789}It's not possible. It's just not.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.58,0:17:18.16,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1036582,1038166}That's right, Nozomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.16,0:17:20.16,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1038166,1040168}Your dad's heard you.\NI'm sure of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.16,0:17:24.04,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1040168,1044047}Do you see, Nozomi-chan? You gotta cheer up\Nand keep singing, for your dad's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.04,0:17:26.04,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1044047,1046049}Of course, for me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.59,0:17:32.01,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1049595,1052014}Oh, I almost forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.63,0:17:36.47,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1052639,1056476}You can bring these to the funeral.\NThe florist didn't make it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.47,0:17:37.97,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1056476,1057978}Thank you, Kuma-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.97,0:17:41.23,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1057978,1061231}Nozomi, you should put these for him.\NHe'd be happy that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.23,0:17:42.39,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1061231,1062399}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.94,0:17:46.73,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:1064943,1066737}Hey, it's Fanni!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.86,0:17:53.07,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1071867,1073076}Hisashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.74,0:17:56.37,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:1073744,1076371}I came as soon as I knew the news.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.37,0:17:57.87,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:1076371,1077873}Let me see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.87,0:17:59.54,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1077873,1079541}I'm so glad that you came.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.25,0:18:03.17,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1082252,1083170}Fanni…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.38,0:18:07.67,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:1086381,1087674}Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.68,0:18:15.64,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:1094681,1095641}Father…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.64,0:18:16.80,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:1095641,1096808}I…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.77,0:18:27.98,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1106777,1107986}It's hot, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.98,0:18:30.44,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1107986,1110447}I brought you beer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.45,0:18:42.12,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:1120457,1122125}Here's to you, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.87,0:18:50.13,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:1125879,1130133}I always wanted to have a drink\Nwith you while you still were alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.80,0:18:55.13,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:1133804,1135138}Alright, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.59,0:18:57.14,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:1135597,1137140}Cheers!
