Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.91,0:19:22.91,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1160914,1162916}{\i1}What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.06,0:19:51.52,Default,Driver,0,0,0,,{TIME:1190068,1191528}Watch it, kid!\NYou have a death wish?!
