Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.45,0:20:41.66,Default,Host,0,0,0,,{TIME:1239451,1241661}What can I do for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.70,0:20:45.66,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1242704,1245665}Anything will do.\NBring me something to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.50,0:20:47.62,Default,Host,0,0,0,,{TIME:1246500,1247626}S-Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.13,0:21:00.59,Default,Guest,0,0,0,,{TIME:1258136,1260597}Hey, where are you from, little girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.97,0:21:02.97,Default,Guest,0,0,0,,{TIME:1260972,1262974}You're soaking wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.97,0:21:04.60,Default,Guest,0,0,0,,{TIME:1262974,1264601}Don't you have\Nanything to dry yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.52,0:21:09.94,Default,Guest,0,0,0,,{TIME:1267521,1269940}Here, you can use this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.94,0:21:13.73,Default,Guest,0,0,0,,{TIME:1271942,1273735}Huh? You don't want it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.73,0:21:16.90,Default,Guest,0,0,0,,{TIME:1273735,1276905}Look at yourself, man.\NIt's way too dirty, hah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.90,0:21:20.28,Default,Guest,0,0,0,,{TIME:1276905,1280283}You think? But it's not\Nas dirty as it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.28,0:21:27.49,Default,Guest,0,0,0,,{TIME:1282285,1287499}By the way, if you look at her,\Nshe looks so much like that new singer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.49,0:21:30.41,Default,Guest,0,0,0,,{TIME:1287499,1290418}I think her name was Kōda Miki?\NShe's super popular now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.41,0:21:32.12,Default,Guest,0,0,0,,{TIME:1290418,1292129}Now that you mention it, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.12,0:21:37.21,Default,Guest,0,0,0,,{TIME:1292129,1297217}Like two peas in a pod.\NBut she can't be the real thing, can she?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.21,0:21:41.13,Default,Guest,0,0,0,,{TIME:1297217,1301138}Kōda Miki was the daughter of\NKōda Conglomerate's president, wasn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.13,0:21:43.84,Default,Guest,0,0,0,,{TIME:1301138,1303849}What possibly would\Nshe be doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.84,0:21:45.30,Default,Guest,0,0,0,,{TIME:1303849,1305308}Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.06,0:21:50.73,Default,Guest,0,0,0,,{TIME:1308061,1310730}Hey, wait up!\NI have your food!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.00,0:22:15.33,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:1333003,1335338}Nozomi-chan, you can go home now.
