Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.01,0:22:32.73,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1348018,1352731}We're not really related, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.73,0:22:34.27,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:1352731,1354274}Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.31,0:22:36.77,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1355317,1356776}In that case…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.77,0:22:38.36,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1356776,1358361}Do you think…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.36,0:22:41.28,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1358361,1361281}I could become your girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.49,0:22:44.28,Default,Fanni,0,0,0,,{TIME:1362490,1364284}Yes.
